### Get All Certificates
GET http://localhost:8080/certificates
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Single Certificate by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/certificates/
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create a New Certificate
POST http://localhost:8080/certificates/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "_id": "cert-software-development",
    "name": "Software Development",
    "description": "A certificate in software development.",
    "requirements": ["Complete all core courses", "Complete a capstone project"],
    "degree": "sftdev-byui",
    "courses": ["course-cs101", "course-cs102", "course-cs103"]
}

###

### Update a Certificate by ID
PUT http://localhost:8080/certificates/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Business Fundamentals",
  "description": "An updated description.",
  "requirements": ["Complete updated core courses"],
  "degreeId": "sftdev-byui",
  "courses": ["course-bus101"]
}

###

### Delete a Certificate
DELETE http://localhost:8080/certificates/
Content-Type: application/json
